title: DefDist DEFCAD Liberator v1.1
description:
The Defense Distributed Liberator v1.1 May 2013

# Files
This is the Liberator v1.1, an update to the Liberator v1.0. This new version also includes SLDPRT and STEP files in addition to STL files. There are also a few different barrels. These files are not being released by Defense Distributed.
